<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>18Day - Your Habit Challenge</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #4361EE;
      --primary-dark: #3A0CA3;
      --accent: #F72585;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --dark: #212529;
      --success: #4CC9F0;
      --gray: #6C757D;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--dark);
      background-color: #f4f5f7;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .logo h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .logo p {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    
    .habit-box {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--dark);
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .challenge-header {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary-dark);
      margin: 35px 0 15px 0;
    }
    
    .commitment {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    
    .commitment ul {
      margin-left: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .commitment li {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 15px 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 35px auto;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary-dark);
    }
    
    .day-progress {
      display: flex;
      margin: 35px 0;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    
    .day {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: #E9ECEF;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--dark);
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .day.critical {
      background-color: var(--accent);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .day:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      height: 3px;
      background-color: #E9ECEF;
      width: 100%;
      left: 100%;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    .day:last-child:after {
      display: none;
    }
    
    .progress-label {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--gray);
    }
    
    .explainer {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 30px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .explainer p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .brain-visual {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    
    .brain-graphic {
      width: 200px;
      height: 150px;
      background-color: #F8F9FA;
      border-radius: 100px 100px 60px 60px;
      position: relative;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border: 2px solid #DEE2E6;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .neural-path {
      position: absolute;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    
    .path-1 {
      width: 30px;
      background-color: var(--success);
      top: 40px;
      left: 40px;
      transform: rotate(30deg);
    }
    
    .path-2 {
      width: 60px;
      background-color: var(--success);
      top: 70px;
      left: 60px;
      transform: rotate(-15deg);
    }
    
    .path-3 {
      width: 80px;
      background-color: var(--success);
      top: 100px;
      left: 50px;
      transform: rotate(20deg);
    }
    
    .path-4 {
      width: 40px;
      background-color: var(--success);
      top: 50px;
      right: 50px;
      transform: rotate(-40deg);
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>18Day</h1>
      <p>The Habit Launchpad</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
      <div class="greeting">
        <p>Hi there!</p>
        <p><strong><%= initiatorEmail %></strong> has invited you to <strong><%= habitDescription %></strong> for 18 days straight!</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="habit-box">
        <%= habitDescription %>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="challenge-header">The 18-Day Challenge</h2>
      
      <div class="commitment">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Research shows 18 days is the critical period for habit formation.</strong></li>
          <li>Daily check-ins to keep you accountable (9pm)</li>
          <li>Support each other through this important phase</li>
          <li>Once you get past this period, the habit is nearly automatic</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="day-progress">
        <div class="day critical">1</div>
        <div class="day critical">6</div>
        <div class="day critical">12</div>
        <div class="day critical">18</div>
        <div class="day">30</div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-label">
        <span>Start</span>
        <span>Critical Period</span>
        <span>Automatic</span>
      </div>
      
      <a href="<%= inviteUrl %>" class="btn">Accept The Challenge</a>
      
      <div class="explainer">
        <p>Once you accept, we'll notify <%= initiatorEmail %> and you'll both start receiving daily check-ins to track your progress through this critical habit-forming period.</p>
        
        <p>After 18 days, your brain will have formed new neural pathways, making this habit much easier to maintain!</p>
        
        <div class="brain-visual">
          <div class="brain-graphic">
            <div class="neural-path path-1"></div>
            <div class="neural-path path-2"></div>
            <div class="neural-path path-3"></div>
            <div class="neural-path path-4"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Based on habit formation research by Phillippa Lally et al., UCL</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>